 persecution: we labour, and have no rest.","year":-588},{"id":"recJWi0GSKWGFazHV","ref":"Lam.5.6","text":"We have given the hand to the Egyptians, and to the Assyrians, to be satisfied with bread.","year":-588},{"id":"recnYvocnijyHxL1M","ref":"Lam.5.7","text":"Our fathers have sinned, and are not; and we have borne their iniquities.","year":-588},{"id":"recgap092xgc4Gkjh","ref":"Lam.5.8","text":"Servants have ruled over us: there is none that doth deliver us out of their hand.","year":-588}]}
